      Uses an inventory in some direction
      if in INSERT: fill our slot from inventory
      if in EXTRACT: move our slot into inventory

  All upgrades should have their action happen in one spot in the router's code. Eg, the part where it transfers stuff....
  put a [+] button in the corner of the UI. This opens another UI, gives you a place to add upgrades. Logistics pipe style.
    
