Slag Furnace:
  CFC Cooblestone, Furnace
  CFC
  CFC
    This furnace functions similarly to a regular furnace. Its extra slots allows additional resources to be extracted from ores. It is 85% as fuel-efficient as a regular furnace, but runs 15% faster.

